  <li>
    <p>The pungency of burning wax, coughs, a stifled sneeze, rose toward Father Paneloux, who, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="reverting to"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(回到某事/继续做某事)</code></b> his <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="\ eg-ˈzȯr-dē-əm \ a beginning or introduction especially to a discourse or composition"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">exordium</code></b> with a subtlety that was much appreciated, went on in a calm, almost <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="being plain, straightforward, or unemotional"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">matter-of-fact</code></b> voice.</p>
  </li>
